             WAIT. YOU MEAN IT?
                  A RAISE?!

04:40.481 --> 04:42.247
       C-COULD YOU GIVE ME
          A RAISE, TOO?

04:42.249 --> 04:43.749
      HEY, KID,
   HERE'S MY CARD!

04:43.751 --> 04:44.883
              HUH?

04:44.885 --> 04:46.752
    H-HEY, KID, COULD YOU GET ME
                  A RAISE, TOO?

04:46.754 --> 04:48.287
        [ ALL SHOUTING ]
          ENOUGH! STOP!

04:48.289 --> 04:49.488
        OOF!
HEY, KIDDO!

04:49.490 --> 04:50.889
      YOU WANT
  TO WEAR MY SUIT?

04:50.891 --> 04:51.890
      HMM? HMM?

04:51.892 --> 04:53.492
       YOU GOT
  TO BE CONFIDENT.

04:53.494 --> 04:55.227
     THAT'S HOW
   YOU REALLY WIN.

