              POINTING FINGERS?

05:13.981 --> 05:16.348
               HOW MANY SALES
           YOU CLOSE TODAY? HUH?

05:16.350 --> 05:17.749
                UH, UH, UH --
                    ZERO!

05:17.751 --> 05:19.985
           SO WHY DON'T YOU TAKE
        THAT SLIMY LITTLE FINGER

05:19.987 --> 05:21.920
