                 HEY, JEFF.
   GUESS WHERE I'M CALLING FROM.

06:24.551 --> 06:25.817
     UH...HOME?

06:25.819 --> 06:27.552
                    NOPE.
                GUESS AGAIN.

06:27.554 --> 06:29.321
   UH, SCHOOL?
                      [ Grunts ]

06:29.323 --> 06:30.689
    GOSH DARN IT!

06:30.691 --> 06:32.324
    YOU STUPID --

06:32.326 --> 06:34.493
