            AND WE BLEW OUR DEAL
     WITH THE FOREIGN INVESTORS.

08:11.925 --> 08:14.025
       I'LL BE DARNED IF SOMEONE
            DOESN'T GET CHOPPED!

08:14.027 --> 08:15.494
        IT --
 IT WAS AN ACCIDENT!

08:15.496 --> 08:18.330
                [ GRUNTING ]

08:18.332 --> 08:20.599
       PLEASE,
I DON'T WANT TO GET CHOPPED.

08:20.601 --> 08:22.434
                    SON,
         I WOULD NEVER FIRE YOU.

08:22.436 --> 08:24.269
                YOU'RE MY SON!
 I AM?

08:24.271 --> 08:27.105
AND ALL THOSE PEOPLE THAT YOU
MET TODAY, THEY'RE JUST SHEEP.

08:27.107 --> 08:28.640
       CHUMPS!
 BUT YOU'RE SPECIAL.

08:28.642 --> 08:30.442
YOU'RE GONNA TAKE OVER
   FOR ME ONE DAY

08:30.444 --> 08:32.043
       AND BE
 THE NEXT BIG BOSS.

08:32.044 --> 08:34.346
 NOW, HELP YOUR POPS
BURN THESE DOCUMENTS.

08:34.347 --> 08:36.214
  WE GOT TO GET RID
OF THIS PAPER TRAIL.

08:36.216 --> 08:37.448
      HUP! HUP!

08:37.451 --> 08:38.817
        UM...

08:38.818 --> 08:40.852
MOM ALWAYS SAID I WASN'T
SUPPOSED TO PLAY WITH FIRE,

08:40.854 --> 08:42.953
 BUT YOU'RE MY DAD,
   I GUESS, SO...

08:42.956 --> 08:44.623
                WHEN YOU MAKE
              THIS MUCH MONEY,

08:44.625 --> 08:46.224
                 YOU CAN DO
         ANYTHING YOU WANT, SON!

08:46.226 --> 08:48.293
                 DING DONG!
      AND GET AWAY WITH IT, TOO!

08:48.295 --> 08:50.028
               [ LAUGHS EVILLY ]
     [ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

