      FREEZE!     FREEZE!
FREEZE!                  FREEZE!

08:51.832 --> 08:54.566
         AAH! AAH! AAH!
         AAH! AAH! AAH!

08:54.568 --> 08:55.800
           AAH. AAH...

08:55.802 --> 08:56.968
              UH...

08:56.970 --> 08:58.303
           HEY, YOU --
            OLD LADY!

08:58.305 --> 09:00.639
       YOU WORK FOR ME --
     JOHN, JEREMY -- WHAT?!

09:00.641 --> 09:02.040
                IT'S JANICE.

09:02.042 --> 09:05.911
          I'VE BEEN WORKING HERE
          FOR OVER FIVE YEARS --

09:05.913 --> 09:08.146
                 UNDERCOVER,
                  THAT IS.

09:08.148 --> 09:11.049
             YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
             FOR BUSINESS FRAUD,

09:11.051 --> 09:14.185
              MONEY LAUNDERING,
           ILLEGAL USE OF MANU--

09:14.187 --> 09:15.587
         NBD! HANDS UP!

09:15.589 --> 09:16.922
        Man:
   COME ON, FITZ!

09:16.924 --> 09:19.157
        Man #2: WAY TO GO, FITZ!
                 WE'RE DONE!

09:19.159 --> 09:21.059
         WAIT A MINUTE.
        WHAT'S GOING ON?

09:21.061 --> 09:22.894
SUIT LOOKS GOOD ON YOU,
        KID.

09:22.896 --> 09:25.830
 BET YOU DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE BUGGED THE WHOLE TIME.

09:25.832 --> 09:27.032
    [ LAUGHING ]

09:27.034 --> 09:28.700
   OH, HONEY COMB,
 THAT WAS SO SMART!

09:28.702 --> 09:30.201
[ SMOOCHES ]
          [ CHUCKLES ]

09:30.203 --> 09:32.771
        COME ON, JANICE.
    NOT IN FRONT OF THE GUYS.

09:32.773 --> 09:35.173
          [ WHISTLING ]

09:35.175 --> 09:37.542
             HELLO?
                       CAREFUL,
                     YOU MAGGOT!

09:37.544 --> 09:39.244
                   THAT'S
               A $4,000 SUIT!

09:39.246 --> 09:40.245
                I'LL EAT YOU!

09:40.247 --> 09:42.581
      BAG 'EM AND TAG 'EM,
              BOYS.

09:42.583 --> 09:45.083
            NBD OUT.

09:46.520 --> 09:48.119
         [ SIREN WAILS ]

09:48.121 --> 09:49.287
